pip install gunicorn

Create procfile
web: gunicorn app:run

To create requirement file:
    pip freeze > requirements.txt

Create git file:
    git init

Add all things to our git:
    git add .

Save/commit the git file
    git commit -am '1st commit for our app'

#heroku cli

to login to heroku
    heroku login

Create the app
    heroku create

rename app
heroku rename <websitename>

push my file to heroku
git push heroku master